        <x-slot name="intro">
            <p class="mb-4">When you exhibit at a trade show, community fair, farmers market, or corporate event, you have approximately three to five seconds to capture the attention of someone walking past your booth. Every visual element of your display — your banner stands, your booth backdrop, your product displays, and your table — contributes to that first impression. A branded table cloth is one of the most cost-effective upgrades you can make to your event display because it replaces a large, unbranded surface with a powerful visual statement that works the moment anyone approaches your table.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Your Table Cloth Is Visible From Across the Room</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">A standard six-foot table cover has approximately twelve square feet of printable surface area — more than most banner stands. That amount of branded real estate, positioned at knee-to-table height, is visible from a significant distance in any event venue. Your logo, your business name, your tagline, and your color scheme displayed on a high-quality custom table cloth can be seen from across the room and draws attendees to your table before they are close enough to read your other marketing materials.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="mid">
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Complete Your Exhibit Display Package</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">A table cloth is a foundational component of any professional event display, and it works best when it is coordinated with your other exhibit elements. When your table cloth, banner stand, and collateral materials all use the same colors, logo placement, and visual style, your booth communicates a level of brand consistency that builds credibility and trust. We produce banner stands, retractable banners, table cloths, table runners, pop-up displays, and event print collateral — all in-house — so we can produce a complete, coordinated exhibit package for your next event.</p>
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Reusable at Every Event</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Unlike one-time use event materials, a quality custom table cloth is designed for repeated use. Our dye sublimation printed table covers are machine washable and maintain their color vibrancy through many wash-and-use cycles. Most businesses and organizations that invest in a custom table cloth use it at every event they exhibit at throughout the year. The per-event cost of a quality table cloth amortizes to almost nothing over a full event season, making it one of the most economical investments in your marketing toolkit.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="lower">
            <h3 class="text-h3 font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Quick Turnaround for Upcoming Events</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">If you have an event coming up soon, contact us as early as possible to allow enough production time for your table cloth. Most custom table cloth orders are completed within three to five business days. If your timeline is tight, ask about our rush production options — we do everything we can to meet urgent deadlines when an important event is approaching. We are used to working with businesses that discover a last-minute exhibit opportunity and need quality materials produced quickly.</p>
        </x-slot>
        <x-slot name="footer">
            <p class="mb-4">We are a veteran owned print shop at 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet, Illinois. We serve businesses and organizations throughout Will County and the greater Chicagoland area with premium custom event display products including table cloths, banner stands, and complete exhibit packages.</p>
            <p>Call us at (815) 349 8600 to discuss your custom table cloth or event display needs today.</p>
        </x-slot>
